symbols.name: Non-Chlorine Bleach When Needed
symbols.description: Only a non-chlorine, color-safe bleach may be used in the laundering process. Chlorine bleach may not be used.

symbols.name: Do Not Bleach
symbols.description: No bleach product may be used. The garment is not colorfast or structurally able to withstand any bleach.

symbols.name: Bleach When Needed
symbols.description: Any commercially available bleach product may be used in the laundering process.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Any Solvent
symbols.description: Dry Clean, any solvent. Usually used with other restrictions on proper dry cleaning procedure.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Petroleum Solvent Only
symbols.description: Dry Clean using only petroleum solvent. Usually used with other restrictions.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Low Heat
symbols.description: May be used with A, P, or F solvent restriction.

symbols.name: Dryclean, No Steam
symbols.description: May be used with A, P, or F solvent restriction.

symbols.name: Do Not Dryclean
symbols.description: Garment may not be commercially drycleaned.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Any Solvent Except Trichloroethylene
symbols.description: Any dry cleaning solvent other than trichloroethylene may be safely used.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Reduced Moisture
symbols.description: May be used with A, P, or F solvent restriction.

symbols.name: Dryclean, Short Cycle
symbols.description: May be used with A, P, or F solvent restriction.

symbols.name: Professional Wet Cleaning Is Not Allowed
Drip Dry in Shade
symbols.description: Hang dripping wet garment from line or bar, in or out doors, without hand shaping or smoothing. Dry away from direct sunlight.

symbols.name: Drip Dry
symbols.description: Hang dripping wet garment from line or bar, in or out doors, without hand shaping or smoothing.

symbols.name: Dry In Shade
symbols.description: Usually added to Line or Drip Dry. Dry away from direct sunlight.

symbols.name: Dry Flat in Shade
symbols.description: Lay out horizontally for drying. Dry away from direct sunlight.

symbols.name: Dry Flat
symbols.description: Lay out horizontally for drying.

symbols.name: Line Dry in Shade
symbols.description: Hang damp garment from line or bar, in or out doors. Dry away from direct sunlight.

symbols.name: Line Dry
symbols.description: Hang damp garment from line or bar, in or out doors.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, High Heat
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a High Heat setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, Low Heat, Gentle
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a maximum of Low Heat and only at the Gentle setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, Low Heat, Permanent Press
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a maximum of Low Heat and only at the Permanent Press setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, Low Heat
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a maximum of Low Heat setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, Medium Heat, Permanent Press
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a maximum of Medium Heat and only at the Permanent Press setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, Medium Heat
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at a maximum of Medium Heat setting.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal, No Heat
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used only at No Heat or Air Only setting.

symbols.name: Do Not Tumble Dry
symbols.description: A machine dryer may not be used. Usually accompanied by an alternate drying method symbol.

symbols.name: Tumble Dry, Normal
symbols.description: A machine dryer may be regularly used at the hottest available temperature setting.

symbols.name: Iron, High
symbols.description: Regular ironing, steam or dry, may be performed at High setting (200C, 290F).

symbols.name: Iron, Low
symbols.description: Regular ironing, steam or dry, may be performed at Low setting (110C, 230F) only.

symbols.name: Iron, Medium
symbols.description: Regular ironing, steam or dry, may be performed at Medium setting (150C, 300F).

symbols.name: Do Not Iron
symbols.description: Item may not be smoothed or finished with an iron.

symbols.name: Do Not Steam
symbols.description: Steam ironing will harm garment, but regular dry ironing at indicated temperature setting is acceptable.

symbols.name: Iron, Any Temperature, Steam or Dry
symbols.description: Regular ironing may be needed and may be performed at any available temperature with or without steam is acceptable.
